              <tp:taxon-name obkms_process="TRUE">   </tp:taxon-name>
              <comment>Basionym. <tp:taxon-name obkms_id="bb4a0219-f0b3-49f5-b772-2b2d71f62b65" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus" reg="Pseudobombax">Pseudobombax</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species" reg="grandiflorum">grandiflorum</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="infraspecific-rank">var.</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="variety" reg="majus">majus</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name> A. Robyns, Bull. Jard. Bot. État Bruxelles 33(1): 56. 1963. — Type: Brazil. Minas Gerais: Viçosa, Chacha Valley, near Chacha House, 17 May 1930, <italic>Y. Mexia 4711</italic> (holotype: F! [F neg. 57390, F0052177F, JSTOR image]; isotypes: BM [BM000645666, JSTOR image], G!, K! [K000913925, JSTOR image], MO! [MO-357466, JSTOR image], NY! [NY133608, JSTOR image], P! [P06622849, JSTOR image], S! [S10-38043], U [U0000789, JSTOR image], US! [US00101966, JSTOR image], VIC!, WIS!). </comment>
